HEADWORD: Dodecahedral
<hw>Do*dec`a*he"dral</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining
to, or like, a dodecahedion; consisting of twelve equal sides.</def>⟦br⟧
